<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>10196</hymn_number>
<title>bḥbk rby yʿzf qlby</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- bḥbk rby yʿzf qlby ạ̉lḥạn frḥ wslạm

[V2]
 thtf nfsy kly lrby qlby wḥby wạlạ̉yạm mḥbty ạ̹lyk rby ạ̉yạ rfyqy fy kl drby

[V3]
 tẖbt qlby bk wzd ḥby lk ạ̉nt ạ̉yạ ḥbyb wlys gẖyrk

[V4]
 2- bḥbk rby ldẖ ḥdytẖy yạ ʿzạʾ nfsy fy ạlậlạm

[V5]
 tsẖfy̱ ʿẓạmy tḥyạ bfrḥ yfyḍ qlby bạlslạm

[V6]
 3- bḥbk rby ạ̉ṭrḥ kẖwfy fy ṣlyb fạdy ạlḥnwn

[V7]
 ḥytẖ dmạk blsm rwḥy tsẖfy jrạḥy wạlsẖjwn

[V8]
 4- bḥbk rby yḥlw lnfsy kwny sfyrạaⁿ llḥbyb

[V9]
 yʿlw ndạỷy hyạ lrby hyạ ạ̹lyh fhw qryb</lyrics>
</song>